@Reasoning
Expose the wrapped list pointer for CV_LIST.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation
Verify kind, load data pointer.
@End Implementation

@Performance_Hints
Time: O(1). Space: O(1).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
